This particle describes the chemical composition of various lipid particles. See also [https://www.wikipathways.org/index.php/Pathway:WP430] for a basic overview of cholesterol synthesis, and for the disease related to the lipoproteins in this pathway see [https://www.wikipathways.org/index.php/Pathway:WP4522].
